<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email - MOUAU ClassMate</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
            color: #374151; 
            max-width: 600px; 
            margin: 0 auto; 
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #ecfdf5 50%, #f0f9ff 100%);
        }
        
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .header { 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1D9D21 0%, #15803d 100%);
            color: white; 
            padding: 40px 30px; 
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1D9D21, #FFF600, #1D9D21);
        }
        
        .logo { 
            font-size: 28px; 
            font-weight: bold; 
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }
        
        .logo-subtitle {
            font-size: 14px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-weight: normal;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        
        .content { 
            padding: 40px 30px; 
        }
        
        .welcome-section {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border-left: 4px solid #1D9D21;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .welcome-section::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            width: 4px;
            height: 100%;
            background: #FFF600;
            border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
        }
        
        .button { 
            display: inline-block; 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1D9D21 0%, #16a34a 100%);
            color: white; 
            padding: 14px 35px; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            border-radius: 8px; 
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(29, 157, 33, 0.25);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .button::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: -100%;
            width: 100%;
            height: 3px;
            background: #FFF600;
            transition: left 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .button:hover::before {
            left: 0;
        }
        
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(29, 157, 33, 0.35);
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #16a34a 0%, #1D9D21 100%);
        }
        
        .link-box {
            background: #f8fafc; 
            padding: 15px; 
            border-radius: 8px; 
            font-size: 14px;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            word-break: break-all;
            margin: 20px 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .link-box::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 3px;
            background: #FFF600;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        
        .footer { 
            text-align: center; 
            margin-top: 40px; 
            padding-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            font-size: 13px; 
            color: #6b7280;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .footer::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 60px;
            height: 3px;
            background: #FFF600;
            border-radius: 3px;
        }
        
        .security-note {
            background: #fffef0;
            padding: 12px 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #FFF600;
            margin: 25px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .user-name {
            color: #1D9D21;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .highlight {
            color: #1D9D21;
            font-weight: 600;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        
        .highlight::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 2px;
            background: #FFF600;
        }
        
        .verification-icon {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background: #FFF600;
            color: #1D9D21;
            border-radius: 50%;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 24px;
            margin-right: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .copy-paste-section {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            margin-top: 25px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .copy-paste-section::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            right: 0;
            width: 4px;
            height: 100%;
            background: #FFF600;
            border-radius: 0 12px 12px 0;
        }
        
        .copy-instructions {
            background: #f0fdf4;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border: 1px solid #bbf7d0;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        
        .step-number {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            background: #1D9D21;
            color: white;
            border-radius: 50%;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 24px;
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
        
        .action-badge {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1D9D21 0%, #15803d 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .action-badge::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 3px;
            background: #FFF600;
        }
        
        .action-badge::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 3px;
            background: #FFF600;
        }
        
        .full-link-box {
            background: #1f2937;
            color: #10b981;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
            border: 1px solid #374151;
            margin: 15px 0;
            position: relative;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        
        .full-link-box::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 3px;
            background: #FFF600;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        
        .step-container {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        
        .step-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #1f2937;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">MOUAU ClassMate</div>
            <div class="logo-subtitle">Your Academic Partner</div>
            <h1 style="margin: 20px 0 0 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600;">Verify Your Email Address</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="welcome-section">
                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px;">Hello <span class="user-name">{{name}}</span>,</p>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">Welcome to the <span class="highlight">MOUAU ClassMate</span> community! We're excited to have you onboard.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="action-badge">
                ‚úâÔ∏è Email Verification Required
            </div>
            
            <p>To complete your registration and start accessing your academic resources, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 35px 0;">
                <a href="{{verificationLink}}" class="button">
                    <span class="verification-icon">‚úì</span>
                    Verify Email Address
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-note">
                <strong>Security Notice:</strong> This verification link will expire in <strong>24 hours</strong> for your protection.
            </div>
            
            <p>If the button doesn't work, you can also copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
            
            <div class="link-box">
                {{verificationLink}}
            </div>
            
            <div class="copy-paste-section">
                <p style="margin: 0 0 20px 0; font-weight: 600; color: #1D9D21; font-size: 18px;">
                    <span class="verification-icon">üìã</span>
                    Copy & Paste Verification
                </p>
                
                <div class="copy-instructions">
                    <p style="margin: 0 0 15px 0; font-weight: 600; color: #15803d;">Follow these simple steps if the button above doesn't work:</p>
                    
                    <div class="step-container">
                        <div class="step-title">
                            <span class="step-number">1</span>
                            Copy the full verification link:
                        </div>
                        <div class="full-link-box">
                            {{verificationLink}}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="step-container">
                        <div class="step-title">
                            <span class="step-number">2</span>
                            Open your web browser
                        </div>
                        <p style="margin: 5px 0 0 0; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">
                            (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge, etc.)
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="step-container">
                        <div class="step-title">
                            <span class="step-number">3</span>
                            Paste the link into your browser's address bar
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="step-container">
                        <div class="step-title">
                            <span class="step-number">4</span>
                            Press Enter to complete your verification
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <p style="margin: 15px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; text-align: center;">
                    <strong>That's it!</strong> The link contains everything needed to verify your email automatically.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 25px;">If you didn't create an account with MOUAU ClassMate, please ignore this email. Your email address will not be used for any communications.</p>
            
            <div class="footer">
                <p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">
                    <strong>MOUAU ClassMate Team</strong><br>
                    Student Management System
                </p>
                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.8;">
                    This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.<br>
                    For assistance, contact our support team through the ClassMate portal.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>